result.title: Baseball Is Back: Some Good News with John Krasinski (Ep. 3)
result.description:
John Krasinski highlights some good news around the world, shares some at-home sports highlights, and surprises some healthcare heroes as a thank you for their hard work and sacrifice.

Thank you to AT&T for their support in offering 3 months of free wireless service to frontline nurses & physicians nationwide. For more info on FirstNet click here: http://go.att.com/HealthcareHeroes

Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center: https://www.bidmc.org/
